Author: lightandempty
Text: yeah, exactly. if it was a girl saying those things i would definitely assume disordered eating of some sort due to media/stereotypes about only girls having ED’s. kinda fucked that it’s like that, but at the same time it’s not like i want guys to have ED’s either, haha

Author: flamingtrashmonster
Text: It’s very possible. It sounds like he at least has ED tendencies and bodily issues. But there could be a number of reasons that explain his behaviour.   But I’m also hesitant to dismiss him having an ED, because I know if this person were a girl I’d automatically want to say she has one.
